<section class="audit rx">
  <div class="w">
    <div class="audit-header">
      <span class="audit-eyebrow">The Process</span>
      <h2 class="audit-title">We Start With an Audit</h2>
      <p class="audit-sub">Before we make recommendations, we understand your situation.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="audit-steps">
      <div class="audit-step rxl d1">
        <div class="step-num">01</div>
        <h3>Marketing Stack Audit</h3>
        <p>We map every tool, platform, and vendor. Find the gaps. Identify what's not connected. See where data lives.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="audit-step rxl d2">
        <div class="step-num">02</div>
        <h3>Intake Process Audit</h3>
        <p>Trace a lead from inquiry to retained client. Where do we lose them? Form → call → consultation → engagement → billing. Every step.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="audit-step rxr d1">
        <div class="step-num">03</div>
        <h3>Marketing Performance Audit</h3>
        <p>Pull 12 months of data. Which channels actually drive retained clients? What's the real cost per client? What's working? What isn't?</p>
      </div>

      <div class="audit-step rxr d2">
        <div class="step-num">04</div>
        <h3>Strategic Planning</h3>
        <p>Based on audit findings, we build a 12-month plan. Set targets. Identify quick wins. Design for long-term growth.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .audit {
    padding: 100px 0;
    background: var(--white);
  }

  .audit-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 80px;
  }

  .audit-eyebrow {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--man);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #5A6577;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .audit-title {
    font-family: var(--man);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: clamp(32px, 6vw, 56px);
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .audit-sub {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--sub);
  }

  .audit-steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .audit-step {
    padding: 40px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FAFAF5 0%, #FFFFFF 100%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(200, 151, 58, 0.1);
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .step-num {
    font-family: var(--bar);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 48px;
    color: rgba(200, 151, 58, 0.2);
    line-height: 0.9;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }

  .audit-step h3 {
    font-family: var(--man);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 20px;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .audit-step p {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--sub);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
</style>
